snippet.title: CUCCCHI - Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore beautiful dioramas and go through dangerous and trippy labyrinths, in a journey inside the paintings of Enzo Cucchi.

Available now on Pc & consoles

Itch.io: https://julian-palacios.itch.io/cuccchi
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1677140/Cuccchi/

Soundtrack by Skinless Lizard: https://eremomusic.bandcamp.com/album/heart-propeller
